		  <div align="left" style="padding-left: 14; padding-right: 14">
		<p>Shining new and warmly welcoming, the Hampton Inn &amp; Suites Albany Downtown is the brightest star on the Albany skyline. The newest hotel in the city, the Hampton Inn &amp; Suites Albany Downtown caters to your every need while keeping you close to the action in the city.</p>
<p>The upscale hotel features 121 lavishly-appointed guest rooms, 35 suites with microwaves and refrigerators, eight whirlpool suites and one executive 2-room suite. The new hotel boasts wired and wireless Internet access, complimentary deluxe On the House™ hot breakfast, on-site exercise facility with sauna and steam room, plenty of meeting space, fresh hot coffee and tea in the lobby 24/7 and, of course, Hilton HHonors® points and miles for your stay. Eleven accessible rooms are available. All rooms and suites are smoke free and feature the Cloud Nine Bedding by Hampton. Welcome to Albany's brightest new star!</p>
<p>Yono's Restaurant, and dp, an American Brasserie, share space near the entrance of the Hampton Inn &amp; Suites! Just a step through the doorway for hotel guests, this upscale fine-dining restaurant features creative continental and Indonesian cuisine for a memorable dining experience. </p>
<p>The Hampton Inn &amp; Suites Albany Downtown is centrally and conveniently located to many downtown attractions, government buildings, and points of interest. The showcase hotel is your gateway to the capital city and all that Albany has to offer including the New York State Capitol, State University at Albany, Pepsi Arena, Capital Repertory Theatre, Albany Palace Theatre, The Egg, New York State Museum, and the Empire State Plaza and Convention Center. Other attractions and points of interest include the nearby Crossgates Shopping Mall, the Albany Riverfront Park, USS Slater and much more.</p>
<p>We’ve Made It Hampton® in downtown Albany and invite you to join us. All reservations booked from this site are guaranteed the best available rate and along with Hilton HHonors® points and miles for any member.<br><br>The hotel features: </p>
<p></p>
<ul>
<li>Cloud Nine Bedding by Hampton (<a href="pdf/1149618319.pdf" target=_blank>read more</a>) 
<li>165 Lavishly Appointed&nbsp;Make It&nbsp;Hampton®&nbsp;Rooms and Suites 
<li>2,300 Square Feet of Meeting and Banquet Rooms 
<li>Yono's Restaurant - Serving Dinner Monday through Saturday 
<li>dp's Ameican Brassiere (Lunch Mon-Fri and Dinner daily) 
<li>Complimentary High-Speed Internet Access 
<li>Daily On-the-House™ Hot Breakfast Buffet 
<li>Fitness Center with Sauna and Steam Room 
<li>Convenience Suite Shop (available 24 hours) 
<li>Hilton HHonors® Program Participation 
<li>Adjacent Parking&nbsp;Facility ($10 / Night)</li></ul>
<p><!--StartFragment -->Hampton Inn and Hampton Inn and Suites have been awarded the "Highest Guest Satisfaction Among Mid-Prices Hotels with Limited Service" by J.D. Power and Associates and named "Best Mid-Priced Hotel Chain (Without Food and Beverage) by Business Travel News. </p>
<p>This wesbite is for the Hampton Inn &amp; Suites Albany Downtown. You may obtain further information regarding Hampton hotels at <a href="http://www.hamptoninn.com/" target=_blank>hamptoninn.com</a>.</p>
